{"tid":1794052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟愚見 -政府不停提黃色經濟圈既原因","createTime":"2019-12-23T00:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T05:05:06.000Z","uid":77937,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0681a4509eb46fffacdeb95036e653260e876c","tid":1794052,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:15:41.000Z","msg":"無錯，黃色經濟圈長遠可以建立民間力量，但短期內對政權未有太大威脅；如果政府唔希望黃色經濟發展，點解仲要日日提起，變相宣傳？<br />\n<br />\n我認為，政府做既野都係個套：轉移焦點<br />\n<br />\n一路以黎，咁多大野發生，對好多人黎講，接收太多資訊，好容易失去焦點。<br />\n<br />\n長遠黎講，黃色經濟圈要搞，工會要搞，但重點都係五大訴求，釋放義士。"},{"pid":"1c994e84a192a83197c26c181e9d37ee43838389","tid":1794052,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"咁港獨呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b478a6d4e9fad42453acef62691e22562eafe1f1","tid":1794052,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c994e84a192a83197c26c181e9d37ee43838389","tid":1794052,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"咁港獨呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:20:59.000Z","msg":"個人認為，一旦涉及分離主義，就會影響國際焦點。香港第一場示威開始中國都話係港獨、顏色革命、分離主義架啦。講得多反而對政權更有利"},{"pid":"c533ffc51415b0ef4de27ebcaf1c3fd7caaffeb2","tid":1794052,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:22:42.000Z","msg":"坦白講，黃色經濟圈係短期內，只會對藍店有影響，希望長期影響會較大"},{"pid":"f00036cf355376b05d0fb355e66cac493aadfb08","tid":1794052,"uid":77937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b478a6d4e9fad42453acef62691e22562eafe1f1","tid":1794052,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c994e84a192a83197c26c181e9d37ee43838389","tid":1794052,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"咁港獨呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T00:20:59.000Z","m